Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:47.80,Default,Komura,0,0,0,,Biar kucarikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:50.43,Default,Komura,0,0,0,,Boleh lihat tasmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:55.68,Default,Komura,0,0,0,,De ....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:58.84,Default,Komura,0,0,0,,Dekatnya!
